Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.70,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(647.622,231.143)}bu gece 9:00'da.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.96,signs,,0,0,0,,Proje
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.97,signs,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H00000E&\c&H00000E&\t(22,2983,\3c&H00000E&\c&H00000E&)\t(2983,3984,\3c&H00000E&\c&H00000E&)\fnBarthowheel\fs109.125\blur1.8\pos(959.973,200.25)\b0}Bölüm 01\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\3c&H00000E&\c&H00000E&\t(22,2983,\3c&H00000E&\c&H00000E&)\t(2983,3984,\3c&H00000E&\c&H00000E&)}Proje'ye Hoş Geldiniz!
